🏗️ GuardAurora Architecture
🧠 Overview

GuardAurora is built as a real-time, AI-driven safety system that combines on-device intelligence with cloud-based services to provide fast, reliable, and scalable protection.

The architecture follows a hybrid model:

⚡ On-device processing → instant threat detection
☁️ Cloud services → communication, storage, intelligence

This ensures low latency, privacy, and resilience in critical situations.

🔧 High-Level Architecture
Mobile App (Client)
│
├── AI Audio Analysis (on-device)
├── Threat Detection Engine
├── GPS Module
├── Voice Assistant / Chatbot
│
├── API Layer
│
Backend (Cloud)
├── Notification Service
├── Real-time Location Service
├── Data Storage
├── AI Model Updates
│
External Services
├── Maps & Routing APIs
├── Emergency Contacts / Authorities
📱 Mobile Application (Client Side)
1. 🎧 Audio Processing Layer
Continuously captures environmental sound (with permission)
Performs real-time preprocessing:
noise filtering
feature extraction (MFCC, spectrograms)

👉 Runs locally on device for speed and privacy

2. 🧠 Threat Detection Engine
Lightweight ML model (e.g. TensorFlow Lite / Core ML)
Detects:
aggression
distress signals
abnormal sound patterns

👉 Key principle:
< 1 second reaction time

3. 🚨 Emergency Trigger System

When a threat is detected:

Starts audio recording
Sends alert signals
Activates GPS tracking

Works automatically without user interaction

4. 📍 GPS & Location Module
Real-time location tracking
Background updates
Optimized for battery efficiency
5. 🤖 AI Assistant Layer
Chatbot + voice interface
Provides:
instructions (“move to a crowded area”)
reassurance
quick actions
☁️ Backend (Cloud Infrastructure)
1. 📡 API Gateway
Secure communication between app and backend
Handles authentication & requests
2. 🔔 Notification Service
Sends:
push notifications
SMS (fallback)
Targets:
trusted contacts
(future) emergency services
3. 📍 Real-Time Location Service
Streams user location
Allows live tracking via secure link
4. 🗄️ Data Storage
Stores:
emergency logs
audio recordings (optional)
user settings

👉 Designed with privacy-first approach

5. 🤖 AI Model Management
Updates detection models
Improves accuracy over time
Supports A/B testing
🧭 Safe Routing System

Uses:

Map APIs
Risk scoring system
How it works:
Assigns “risk level” to areas based on:
time of day
historical data (future)
user reports (future)

👉 Outputs:
Safer alternative routes

🔐 Security & Privacy
End-to-end encryption for sensitive data
On-device processing minimizes data sharing
User-controlled permissions
No continuous cloud audio streaming
⚡ Key Design Principles
1. Speed First
Detection must be instant
No reliance on network for core safety features
2. Privacy by Design
Audio processed locally
Minimal data storage
3. Fail-Safe System
Works even with:
low internet
limited battery
4. Scalability
Cloud designed to support:
thousands → millions of users
🔮 Future Architecture Evolution
Edge AI improvements
Integration with wearables (smartwatch, panic button)
Federated learning (privacy-preserving AI training)
Real-time community threat map
